{"tid":1911123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"卑詩省老婦確診染病 加國官員相信在香港受感染","createTime":"2020-03-05T06:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T06:53:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1294d77840f2a37f9565fcdc1f466e6063324274","tid":1911123,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"卑詩省老婦確診染病 加國官員相信在香港受感染<br />\n<br />\n加拿大卑詩省一名曾經到香港旅遊的81歲老婦，感染<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">新型冠狀病毒</span></del>武漢肺炎，目前在溫哥華一間醫院接受隔離治療，情況危殆。衛生官員表示，患者本身有長期病患，<span style=\"color: gold;\">早前組團到印度及香港旅遊，上星期回國</span>，數日後出現病徵。官員指印度只有零星病例，<span style=\"color: gold;\">根據患者出現病徵的時間，懷疑她在香港受感染</span>，已將個案通知香港衛生部門，並追蹤同團的人。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大至今確診34宗新型冠狀病毒個案，有13宗在卑詩省。國防部宣布，軍方為疫情大流行進行預備工作，會暫停非緊急派遣任務，如有需要將會派往疫區，協助撤僑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1271670&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1271670%26csid%3D261_367&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=88998fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1271670&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"bda9d137c1d78a6369e0823ab6220e0d4576d0c1","tid":1911123,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"印度佬中嘅機會大d"},{"pid":"dd51ca2647855178c03a427a8bcf51b34d0e461b","tid":1911123,"uid":325098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bda9d137c1d78a6369e0823ab6220e0d4576d0c1","tid":1911123,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"印度佬中嘅機會大d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:49:57.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n香港人做到咁<br />\n仲點會感染佢"},{"pid":"b1fe0a4402e677e621b6d07070ea5c3ad9b9b39c","tid":1911123,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"????香港個個口罩..."}]}